query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CAB.NUNOTA) AS TOTAL_PEDIDOS_CONFIRMADOS FROM TGFCAB CAB JOIN TGFITE I ON I.NUNOTA = CAB.NUNOTA AND I.CODEMP = CAB.CODEMP WHERE I.CODPROD = 9558 AND CAB.TIPMOV = 'O' AND CAB.STATUSNOTA = 'L' AND CAB.DTNEG BETWEEN '2025-10-01' AND '2025-12-31' AND CAB.CODUSUINC IN (104,107,263,309);
